## Run auth.http → Login first to populate {{token}}

### Get full inventory (equipment + backpack + weight)
GET {{host}}/inventory
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Pick up a Health Potion
POST {{host}}/inventory/pick-up
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "health-potion",
  "quantity": 3
}

### Pick up a Mana Potion
POST {{host}}/inventory/pick-up
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "mana-potion",
  "quantity": 3
}

### Pick up an Iron Longsword
POST {{host}}/inventory/pick-up
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "iron-longsword",
  "quantity": 1
}

### Equip Iron Longsword to weapon slot
POST {{host}}/inventory/equip
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "iron-longsword"
}

### Unequip weapon slot
POST {{host}}/inventory/unequip
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "slot": "weapon"
}

### Drop an item from backpack
POST {{host}}/inventory/drop
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "health-potion",
  "quantity": 1
}

### Use a Health Potion
POST {{host}}/inventory/use
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "health-potion"
}

### Use a Mana Potion
POST {{host}}/inventory/use
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "mana-potion"
}

###
## ─── Spell Scrolls (learn level 4-5 spells via items) ───
###

### Pick up a Scroll of Counterspell (mage, level 4)
POST {{host}}/inventory/pick-up
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "scroll-of-counterspell",
  "quantity": 1
}

### Use Scroll of Counterspell — should learn Counterspell
POST {{host}}/inventory/use
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "scroll-of-counterspell"
}

